{"type": "article", "id": 2508, "title": "Adidas Originals ＝Pharrel Williams", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-23T08:47:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1051, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 15, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232528b4gmpi1HyvMTSdBk.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>自从去年夏天成为优衣库 UT 代言人之后，美国音乐人 </span><span>Pharrell Williams 就在时尚圈特别吃得开。最近他发布了个人和 Adidas Originals 的首个合作系列。该系列包括 Adidas 经典的 Stan Smith 鞋款和真皮棒球衫，分别推出了蓝色、黑色和红色三个版本。Williams 还把 Adidas 的三道杠 Logo 转化成了等号“＝”，街头感十足，又传递了平等自由的理念。Stan Smith 鞋款定价 150 美元，皮衣定价 1000 美元，9 月 20 日起已在全球各大门店上市，<a href=\"http://packershoes.com/collections/adidas?page=1\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买。</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><a href=\"http://packershoes.com/collections/adidas?page=1\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232527fbTBj0L8wQiy6u5k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.490625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232527Kl2Y8EuLUWnTvj1a.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.546875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232528IqUkscapMQRJKxzF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a><a href=\"http://packershoes.com/collections/adidas?page=1\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232528zGO1p60c5PWMFu9q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></a></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}